  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Collections of heavy boulders tumble to the ground at four different points you can see within range. Each creature in a 20-foot-radius sphere centered on each point you choose must make a <strong>Dexterity saving throw</strong>. The sphere spreads around corners. A creature takes <strong>12d8 bludgeoning damage</strong> on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one. A creature in the area of more than one burst is affected only once.</p><p>The spell damages objects in the area that aren't being worn or carried.</p>",
